 KIND WORDS BLUES"]

00:54:43.340 --> 00:54:46.320
It was a privilege being
able to talk with you today.

00:54:46.320 --> 00:54:47.560
Thank you for coming.

00:54:47.560 --> 00:54:50.610
[APPLAUSE]

